Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:37.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:94860,97460}There's this boy I'd like to meet,\Nnamed Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:40.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98470,100300}Is he in this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:48.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105950,108550}A First Rendezvous of Tears?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:56.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114770,116970}I've finally found you!\NAsuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120780,122180}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.69,0:02:04.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122690,124680}H... hey, what are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:07.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124960,127020}I looked all over town for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:10.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128100,130090}But what are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130200,132930}It took so long to find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:17.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133580,137040}I guess I couldn't find you,\Nsince you're so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:20.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137220,140380}Answer my question,\Nbefore this turns into a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141560,143590}Meimi, who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:24.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143730,144990}She's a new student!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:27.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145130,147070}I'll tell you about her later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:31.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148210,151570}I guess she doesn't need me\Nto take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152250,153410}Some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:35.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154350,155250}Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:40.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158830,160300}Cute... cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160400,161660}Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161770,163330}Relax. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164170,165870}What is with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170220,172710}"Rina Takamiya"\NI'm Rina Takamiya,\Na new student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:53.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172860,173950}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178300,180570}Asuka, why don't you show me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:01.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180710,181800}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:05.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181940,185400}Why not?! You should be\Nnice to new students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185580,187850}She's cool, I like tall girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188090,189720}She doesn't look 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:11.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190130,191680}She's got a nice figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192000,193730}Maybe she's a model, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:17.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194100,197230}Stop! You over there!\NDon't go making assumptions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197340,198670}She heard us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:24.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200280,204270}When I grow up, I'm going to\Nbecome a police officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205120,206520}A police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:29.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206690,209860}That's right.\NI'm going to catch bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:35.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211500,215530}Especially that sneaky thief,\NSt. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215980,217880}I'm going to arrest her with\Nmy bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220420,221610}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:43.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221960,223980}I'm the one who's going\Nto arrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:47.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224560,227860}Well, Ms. Takamiya, Asuka Jr. was\Nappointed by the mayor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:51.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228070,231060}to investigate St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233080,235240}Well, the Mayor happens\Nto be my Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:59.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235350,239250}The Mayor's Niece.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240090,242930}That's right?\NIs... that... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:06.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243740,246700}Then I'll go right over and ask\Nmy Uncle for permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:10.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247780,250110}There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:12.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250150,252910}St. Tail won't be captured\Nthat easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254190,255050}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255090,256890}Poor thing, you're trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257460,259860}What's with her,\Nsticking so close to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:22.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259970,262800}Humph! Suit yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:23.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263140,263840}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:30.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269190,270650}Ancient Hidden Treasures Exhibition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:34.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271320,274780}Yes, it's being held now\Nat the Central Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:35.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275100,275930}The problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:39.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276370,279030}The "Dagger of Yatto"\Nthat's on display...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279540,281130}is not what it seems to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281910,283540}It's not a hidden treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284180,285010}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:47.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285520,287080}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287260,289990}The dagger is a copy\Nthat I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290400,292130}It's a replica!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:55.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292840,295960}Replica... you mean it's a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296540,299740}I usually work as a sculptor...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:04.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300450,304050}But one day, I was asked by the man\Nin charge of Central Hall, Mr. Mizutani...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:07.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304560,307790}to make a replica of the\NDagger of Yatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:13.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308870,313030}I made it because he promised me that\Nhe was only going to use it as...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313680,316580}a decoration in his house,\Njust to enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317080,320180}I never thought he would exhibit it\Nas the real Dagger of Yatto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320930,323660}If I report it to the police,\NI'll probably be arrested, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:29.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324630,329430}I can't sleep at night because I think\Nabout everybody I'm deceiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330080,331870}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338030,340390}The Lord will surely forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:43.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341030,343560}After all, you've confessed\Nand repented.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:45.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344610,345700}Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:50.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346450,350470}Don't worry. I'm sure the Lord\Nwill guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357370,359840}So that's the story, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360510,361530}Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:04.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361980,364310}I don't know much about\Nancient relics...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:08.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364720,368310}whether it's Jomon period earthenware,\Na burial mound figure, or a clay doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368360,370520}you can count on\NSt. Tail to recover it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:12.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371130,372190}Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372560,374000}it's a dagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:18.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374640,378940}I've got an idea of how things are\Nbetween you and Ms. Takamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379310,380280}but try to stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383290,385120}I'll show her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393470,395070}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396180,397650}Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:41.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397780,401950}Meimi, I'm quite sure my magic\Ntrick will work this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402460,403650}Want to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:49.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403930,409130}Not right now. But, could I\Nborrow one of your magic tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410310,411970}One of my magic tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:02.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418990,422930}I'm going to send him a warning\Nthat will blow his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:09.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426040,429370}Asuka!\NCan I eat lunch with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:15.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430780,435050}No way!\NGirls always want to trade snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:17.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435390,437360}I'm not interested in doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441270,442240}What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:28.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444850,448250}"I'm going to Central Hall tonight\Nto get the Dagger of Yatto..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:29.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448290,449620}"St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:34.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450820,454560}For a thief, she sure does send\Nlovely warnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:35.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454870,455920}Doesn't she Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455970,457200}Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457300,458360}What was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:39.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458410,459340}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:44.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461910,464510}It's a warning from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464550,465420}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:47.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465550,467150}Let me taste some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468590,470960}Hey don't eat it!\NIt's my lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471430,474160}What are you talking about?\NDon't hog it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474240,476670}-Hey don't eat my hand!\N-Let go!!\NWhat is with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477880,479210}Your chopsticks broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479320,481080}Yes, it seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:12.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489570,492130}I've been waiting for you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:15.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492380,495570}My name is Mizutani and I'm the\None in charge of this exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496380,497870}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:20.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498250,500120}The pleasure is mine, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:22.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500460,502760}Let's get down to business.\NMay I see the Dagger of Yatto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:23.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502830,503560}Please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:35.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511880,515940}It's almost like a movie set.\NAll this justfor the exhibition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:41.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516490,521900}Yes, I even have a special exhibition\Nroom just for the Dagger of Yatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522200,523430}This way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:53.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528050,533580}It's inside this pyramid set.\NWe've set up a room in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:01.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538240,541260}If the dagger is stolen and\Nthere's an investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:17.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553300,557130}The cameras are on 24 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:18.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557470,558570}Asuka Jr. ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:23.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558610,563780}Are there any particular orders\Nyou have for the guards on duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:27.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564220,567880}Shall we guard it\Nfrom inside the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:31.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568300,571630}No... just guard the entrance\Nof the exhibition hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:33.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572110,573300}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576950,580250}I'll hide inside that Sarcophagus,\Nif it's ok with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580350,581720}Huh? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:47.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582460,587900}St. Tail usually appears from above.\NSo this should give me a good view.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:51.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588740,591800}We'll make her think this place\Nis not heavily guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591850,594910}When she comes in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:57.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594950,597280}I'll catch her in the act and\Narrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:00.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599630,600990}This set is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:03.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601360,603590}The place is narrow, so I'll get\Nher for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603940,605630}Not clever enough, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:07.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606840,607900}Takamiya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611690,613810}You've got to trap her\Nmore aggressively.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:15.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614190,615950}It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616260,617750}You're bothering me,\Nso go on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618030,620970}Hmm... You really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:24.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623280,624900}Wh... what?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625010,626380}"To Askua Jr. ..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:29.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626420,629250}"Please look after my niece, Rina.\NI'm sure she'll be able to help you."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:31.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629290,631190}"Please let her assist you."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631730,633820}Mayor Hideo Morinaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:42.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636670,642730}I'll be in the surveillance room,\Nwatching for your strategy to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:45.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644750,645620}Darn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:50.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645720,650350}But with my strategy, tonight will be\Nthe last night for St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:52.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650770,652100}Who said that you could...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:53.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652640,653860}Read... Read...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:28.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685270,688500}Forgive me, for I use\Nno gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693920,695050}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697360,698420}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700400,702260}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725120,726520}Be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726620,728380}Especially for Ms. Takamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:15.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732600,735930}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:28.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744320,748850}I won't lose tonight's fight.\NThey will see my victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:52.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770380,772370}They're only guarding the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:55.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772580,775740}That's pretty lenient, considering\Nthey're up against St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782100,783190}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:13.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791090,793180}So that's the Dagger of Yatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796500,797290}It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:20.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797330,800090}Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806250,808380}Rina, the security camera!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809090,810420}What did you say!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814600,816930}How could this happen at\Nsuch a critical moment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817000,819000}Please Stand By.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824920,826980}She's here...\NSt. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:53.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830030,833400}That's right, as soon as you touch\Nthat case, you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:00.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838450,840380}Wait a moment, Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:02.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840450,842780}She's got to be kidding,\Nnot taking us seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842860,845690}I can't count on Asuka's strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:10.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848770,850960}Set target: Inside the pyramid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:17.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856720,857650}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858690,860660}That's as far as you go, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:30.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867170,870400}Asuka, it'll all be over in a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877130,878680}Let me see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881170,882160}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888520,890680}What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:00.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899570,900670}Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:15.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912100,915070}There, now the gas will\Nfill the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915100,917940}You can't escape now, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932510,935000}Try not to... breathe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935080,937510}as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940120,941890}He'll see my face...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943200,945720}I've got to get out of here!\NTake it easy Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946200,948430}But... I can 't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949340,951280}Aren't you going to flee, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952150,953980}Maybe I'll get to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956220,958950}It's no use... I can't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960600,962120}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962270,963430}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:10.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968450,970880}My eyes are so teary,\NI can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:16.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975060,976620}I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976760,978130}Tear gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980870,982630}It should have worked by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:29.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987020,989680}What the hell is he doing with her?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:40.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997710,1000570}St. Tail!\NWhere is St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:42.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000880,1002850}There couldn't have been a better\Nopportunity to catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:44.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002880,1004150}What were you doing?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:48.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004420,1008410}Idiot! "What were you doing!"\Nis something I should be asking you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:51.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008490,1011160}I thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:53.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011200,1013630}Killed you, my foot!\NYou two were hugging each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017250,1019410}Rina! The Dagger of Yatto\Nhas been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024830,1026520}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026800,1028030}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:12.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029300,1032430}I'm sorry, but I'm taking\Nthe dagger with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:23.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042360,1043160}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043430,1044400}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:26.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044500,1046090}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047980,1049140}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:42.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059000,1062370}Goodbye Mr. Detective.\NIt's been fun, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:49.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066650,1069170}She did it again, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069450,1071980}Damn it! Show me you face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072020,1073420}St. Tail!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:56.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073860,1076350}Hey you, what do you think\Nyou're looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:18:00.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077040,1080330}Thanks to you, I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080640,1082130}Stupid! Stupid! Super Stupid!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082650,1084050}Who are you calling stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:07.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084250,1087650}We could've caught her,\Nif you held onto her tighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:12.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088660,1092090}I don't want to have to use\Ntear gas to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092230,1093430}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093800,1095790}I'll say this one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:18.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095840,1098360}I'm the one who will capture\NSt. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098510,1100170}Suit yourself! Humph!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:22.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100580,1102170}Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102350,1103010}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:42.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119450,1122910}I left security for this place\Nup to him because he's your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122960,1124490}I trusted him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:45.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124530,1125930}Are you listening to me?!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:48.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125970,1128530}Do you know how valuable the\NDagger of Yatto is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:50.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128570,1130970}both as an archeological\Nand artistic treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:53.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131450,1133680}It's so valuable, that no monetary\Nvalue could be placed on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:56.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133780,1136720}How are the police going to take\Nresponsibility for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:19:02.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137690,1142030}Ah... it's a nice painting.\NDon't tell me this is an imitation, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143000,1144060}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144710,1146500}I've already investigated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:11.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146540,1151340}I hear that your Dagger of Yatto\Nis a genuine replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:15.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152990,1155360}Getting the police involved\Nin your conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:18.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155390,1158730}that's taking it a bit too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:28.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165450,1168940}"IT WAS A FAKE!"\NWhat a stupid thief,\Nstealing a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:32.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169860,1172950}She ends up stealing for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:35.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174200,1175360}That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175400,1176100}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177910,1179600}She knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:43.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179640,1183100}She probably was helping\Nsomebody out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183380,1185150}Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:47.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185190,1187950}And just how would you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:49.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188230,1189160}I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:53.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190470,1193060}because I've been chasing\Nher all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:56.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194010,1196200}Oh, is that so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:20:01.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197080,1201680}St. Tail, I'll reveal your\Ntrue identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:10.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207570,1210040}You were crying last night,\Nweren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215850,1217510}How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:19.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217590,1219560}'Cause your eyes are red.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:22.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220560,1222320}Why did you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:23.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222460,1223590}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223730,1225330}Hey, tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226610,1228730}It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:31.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229650,1231710}Men have a lot things to\Nattend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:38.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235320,1238920}I know, it's because you're always\Ndedicated to the job you 're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:41.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239430,1241260}It's because you're kind.
